            "text_content": "<p>Peroxide is effective, but it whitens by oxidising through the enamel — which is exactly why strips can sting. PAP+ lifts stains on a peroxide-free pathway, so most people can whiten daily without the zingers.</p><p><strong>How does it work?</strong></p><p>You load a ribbon of PAP+ gel into the tray, bite down and switch the LED on. Ten minutes later you rinse. The purple pigment colour-corrects on the surface straight away; the PAP keeps working on stains underneath over your daily sessions.</p><p>Most people notice a cleaner, smoother feel in the first few days, and their first shade-card movement inside the first week or two. Individual results vary — that's why we tell you to photograph day one and check the shade card each Sunday.</p>",
